Class SCStruct

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tub.pes.syscir.sc_model.SCStruct
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SCModule

    public class SCStruct
extends java.lang.Object
    this represents a SystemC-Struct, it contains variables, functions, a constructor, a list of fathers and a marker if its a channel or not
